  "description": {
    "zh": "向你问好。现在忙吗，士兵？希望不忙，因为我有事交给你。那个一直和你合作的姑娘也表示愿意帮忙。那我就直说了……\n\n我有个朋友，也是个商人，同样前俄国军人出身。他特别痴迷现代俄式武器和装备，对那种靠得住的老家伙嗤之以鼻，没错，就是那种人。总之，我想向他证明苏联时代的东西照样靠得住，但我眼下实在抽不出时间和精力。\n\n这时候就该你上场了，你是干这事的最佳人选，可别让我失望！我给你列了张单子，带上这些东西，去射翻一群敌人，甭管是谁。顺便说一句，你上次带给 Lotus 的那些枪状态都挺好，我可以借你几支用来完成这次任务。\n\n具体用哪款枪我觉得无所谓，带侧轨的、带消音器的，随便，只要不是那些现代型号就行。祝你好运，士兵。\n\nSpecified Gear :\n - Any Russian / Soviet Firearm made before the 1990s\n - Tank Crew Helmet / SSh-68 / SSSh-94 SFERA-S / Altyn / Maska-1SCh / ZSh-1-2M Helmet\n - 6B2 / 6B13 / 6B23 / 6B5 Zh-86 Uley / 6B3TM-01 Armored Vest",
    "en": "Greetings. Are you busy right now, warrior? I hope not, because I got something for you. That one girl you have been working with offered her help aswell. Let me get to the point now...\n\nI have this one friend, also a dealer and also ex-russian military. So he is really into the modern russian weapons and gear, he despises the old reliable stuff, yeah one of those people. Anyway, I would like to prove to him that the stuff from the USSR is still reliable, however I don't have any time and resources on my hand currently.\n\nNow this is where you come into place, you are perfect for this job so don't disappoint me! I made a list for you, take these things, shoot up a bunch of hostiles with it, doesn't matter who. And by the way, the guns you brought to Lotus last time are in good condition. I can lend you a few to use them for this job.\n\nI don't think it matters what exact variant of the guns you use, with a siderail, with a suppressor, whatever I don't care as long as it's not one of the modern ones. Good luck out there warrior.\n\nSpecified Gear :\n - Any Russian / Soviet Firearm made before the 1990s\n - Tank Crew Helmet / SSh-68 / SSSh-94 SFERA-S / Altyn / Maska-1SCh / ZSh-1-2M Helmet\n - 6B2 / 6B13 / 6B23 / 6B5 Zh-86 Uley / 6B3TM-01 Armored Vest"
  },
